  "commentary": "With SPX at 7016.52 sitting right between the massive +22962.6M gamma wall at 7025 and the +13563.5M wall at 7000, dealers are in active hedging mode following the recent wall break event. The PIN regime confirms dealers are long gamma and will be selling this bounce into the 7025 resistance zone while providing support on any dip toward the 7000 level. Watch for mean reversion behavior with 7025 acting as a hard ceiling where dealer selling intensifies, and 7000 as the key support where dealer buying kicks in.\n\nBottom line: expect price to get pinned between 7000-7025 with resistance at the top.",
